These are Puzzles for 5x4 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 5x4-Level-4-1::.
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: zinnia, sunflower, azalea, iris
4 different games are played: poker, scrabble, whist, chess
The people have 4 different hobbies: sudoku, magic-tricks, woodworking, skydiving
There 4 different types of food: radish, avocado, lime, watermelon
City: edinburgh, marseilles, berlin, prague
 1. the person who growszinnia is on the far left or far right##3
 2. the person traveling to berlin is on the right of the person eating radish##1
 3. the person traveling to prague is on the left of the person traveling to marseilles##1
 4. the person playing whist is in an odd position##4
 5. the person playing chess is the person playing chess##1
 6. the person traveling to berlin is on the far right##1
 7. the person eating lime is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is skydiving##3
 8. the person traveling to edinburgh is on the left of the person eating avocado##1
 9. the person who growsazalea is on the left or right of the person playing scrabble##3
10. the person playing poker is on the left or right of the person playing whist##3
11. the person who growszinnia is on the left of the person playing chess##1
12. the person who's hobby is woodworking is between the person playing whist and the person who's hobby is magic-tricks##2
13. the person who growsazalea is the person traveling to prague##1
14. the person traveling to berlin is the person who growssunflower##1
15. the person who's hobby is skydiving is on the left or right of the person who growssunflower##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2     |     3      |     4      |
| Flower           | zinnia | azalea | iris  | sunflower    |
| Game   | scrabble     | chess   | whist  | poker  |
| Hobby           | magic-tricks        | woodworking    | skydiving        | sudoku |
| Food         | watermelon    | avocado      | radish   | lime    |
| City     | edinburgh  | prague     | marseilles | berlin |

