.:: Puzzle 5x4-Level-4-2::.
City: hannover, paris, san-francisco, colone
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: august, october, january, july
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: aconite, orchid, daisy, iris
4 different games are played: chess, canasta, go, monopoly
There are 4 different nationalities: australian, canadian, german, indian
 1. the australian is on the left of the person who growsorchid##1
 2. the person traveling to paris is on the right of the person who growsorchid##1
 3. the person traveling to hannover is in an odd position##4
 4. the person playing monopoly is on the left of the german##1
 5. the person who growsiris is the canadian##1
 6. the person who's birthday is in january is on the far left##1
 7. the person traveling to colone is in an even position##4
 8. the person who's birthday is in january is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in october##3
 9. the person who growsiris is on the left or right of the person traveling to colone##3
10. the person who's birthday is in august is the indian##1
11. the person traveling to san-francisco is on the far left##1
12. the person playing chess is on the left of the person who growsaconite##1
13. the person playing canasta is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |      2       |    3    |      4      |
| City      | san-francisco        | colone       | hannover    | paris       |
| Birthday         | january | october      | july | august |
| Flower   | iris     | daisy | orchid  | aconite   |
| Game   | canasta   | monopoly         | chess   | go      |
| Nationality         | canadian      | australian     | german    | indian      |

