.:: Puzzle 5x4-Level-4-3::.
There are 4 different favourite colors: yellow, apricot, aquamarine, white
There are 4 different favourite beverages: lemonade, cola, mirinda, soy-milk
House: townhouse, art-deco, ranch-style, craftsman
4 different pets are kept: chinchilla, frog, hamster, goldfish
There are 4 different nationalities: thai, dutch, egyptian, polish
 1. the owner of the frog is the art-deco house##1
 2. the art-deco house is on the left of the thai##1
 3. the polish is in an odd position##4
 4. the owner of the chinchilla is on the left or right of the person drinking lemonade##3
 5. the egyptian is on the left or right of the person who likes apricot##3
 6. the owner of the frog is on the left or right of the owner of the hamster##3
 7. the person drinking soy-milk is on the left or right of the ranch-style house##3
 8. the thai is on the right of the polish##1
 9. the owner of the frog is in an odd position##4
10. the person who likes aquamarine is the ranch-style house##1
11. the craftsman house is on the left of the owner of the frog##1
12. the craftsman house is on the right of the person drinking mirinda##1
13. the owner of the hamster is the person who likes white##1
14. the ranch-style house is on the left of the person who likes apricot##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |     2     |     3     |     4     |
| Color          | aquamarine | apricot | yellow     | white |
| Beverage           | mirinda  | soy-milk   | lemonade | cola  |
| House   | ranch-style  | craftsman      | art-deco     | townhouse   |
| Pet         | goldfish | chinchilla  | frog   | hamster    |
| Nationality     | egyptian | dutch    | polish     | thai |

