 2. the fonseca-smoker is the person who likes green##1
 3. the person who likes grey is on the left or right of the ritmeester-smoker##3
 4. the swisher-smoker is between the nigerian and the dutch##2
 5. the person who growssunflower is on the far left##1
 6. the dutch is on the left of the person who likes mauve##1
