 8. the person who growsbegonia is the japanese##1
 9. the ritmeester-smoker is on the left or right of the aristoff-smoker##3
10. the person watching family movies is on the left of the person watching romance movies##1
11. the person watching fantasy movies is in an odd position##4
12. the person who likes mauve is the person watching fantasy movies##1
13. the person watching fantasy movies is on the left or right of the person who likes grey##3
14. the person watching family movies is on the left or right of the person watching romance movies##3
15. the person watching zombie movies is on the far right##1

