The people have 4 different hobbies: card-games, puzzles, video-games, cooking
 1. the person who's hobby is cooking is between the person who's hobby is video-games and the person playing billiard##2
 2. the fan of rock is in an even position##4
 3. the bolivar-smoker is on the right of the fan of rock##1
 4. the fan of funk is in an even position##4
 5. the person who growsdahlia is on the right of the person who's hobby is puzzles##1
