 8. the person who's hobby is cooking is on the left or right of the person who growsdahlia##3
 9. the fan of pop is the person playing backgammon##1
10. the person playing billiard is the swisher-smoker##1
11. the fan of pop is the baccarat-smoker##1
12. the person who growsazalea is the bolivar-smoker##1
13. the person who growsdahlia is in an even position##4
14. the person playing billiard is the fan of funk##1

.:: Answer ::.
