 3. the person playing domino is on the right of the person who growsmarigold##1
 4. the person driving the car is in an odd position##4
 5. the person who growszinnia is the person playing domino##1
 6. the person driving the tram is on the left of the owner of the lizard##1
 7. the person who growsmarigold is the person playing scrabble##1
 8. the person driving the airplane is the owner of the lizard##1
 9. the person playing backgammon is on the far left or far right##3
10. the person who's sport is weightlifting is the owner of the turtle##1
11. the person who growsmarigold is in an odd position##4
12. the person who's sport is badminton is on the left of the person who growsrose##1
13. the person who's sport is badminton is in an odd position##4
14. the person driving the airplane is between the person who's sport is weightlifting and the person playing backgammon##2

