 8. the freelancer is on the right of the person drinking milk##1
 9. the cape-cod house is on the far left##1
10. the person who likes brown is between the person who's sport is ice-hockey and the person drinking tea##2
11. the doctor is on the right of the person drinking water##1
12. the person who likes emerald is on the right of the ranch-style house##1
13. the person drinking milk is on the left or right of the farmhouse house##3
14. the person who likes brown is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2      |     3      |    4     |
| Beverage         | water | fanta  | milk | tea  |
| Sport   | sailing     | ice-hockey    | climbing     | lacrosse      |
| Job   | designer  | doctor  | mechanic     | freelancer |
| House           | cape-cod      | palace | ranch-style       | farmhouse     |
| Color     | mauve      | red | brown  | emerald   |

